description:
Are you tired of Christian books? They may have taken on the look of self-help books, but some Christian books are inspired by the Holy Spirit–and we cannot doubt that! Join Pastor Ted Wilson as he embarks on a journey through #TheGreatControversy by #EllenWhite.  #Shorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ #YouTubeShorts​​​​​​​​​​​​​​ 

To watch the full video from Elder Wilson, paste this link into your browser: https://youtu.be/LF6pjueQsHI?si=j7EcgF7HIf7P6unt .
